   "translit": "prabh tujh binaa nahee tthaau |",
   "english": "Without You, God, I have no place at all.",
   "shabadId": "0TH"
  },
  {
   "gurmukhi": "ਨਾਨਕਾ ਬਲਿ ਬਲਿ ਜਾਉ ॥੨॥",
   "translit": "naanakaa bal bal jaau |2|",
   "english": "Nanak is a sacrifice, a sacrifice to You. ||2||",
   "shabadId": "0TH"
  },
  {
