   "translit": "geh bhujaa prabh jee lehu |",
   "english": "Please take my hand, and save me, Dear God.",
   "shabadId": "0TH"
  },
  {
   "gurmukhi": "ਲੋਭਿ ਮੋਹਿ ਬਾਧੀ ਦੇਹ ॥",
   "translit": "lobh mohi baadhee deh |",
   "english": "The human body is in the grip of greed and attachment.",
   "shabadId": "0TH"
  },
  {
